  "title": "Town Council Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage and supervise estate maintenance operations</li><li>Oversee conservancy works, cleaning services, landscaping, and contractors</li><li>Handle resident/stakeholder enquiries, feedback, and complaints professionally</li><li>Conduct site inspections, identify defects and ensure timely rectification</li><li>Coordinate preventive and corrective maintenance works</li><li>Monitor service providers’ performance and ensure compliance with standards</li><li>Support planning, budgeting and reporting activities</li><li>Prepare and submit operational reports and documentation</li><li>Liaise with authorities, vendors and internal departments on estate matters</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma / Degree in Estate Management, Facilities Management or equivalent</li><li>Minimum 5 years’ experience in estate or property management</li><li>Strong understanding of maintenance coordination, vendor management & site supervision</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Able to work independently, solve problems, and manage multiple tasks</li><li>Proficient in MS Office and basic reporting</li></ul>",
